{"id": "ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8", "rating": 4.8, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 3199, "displayName": {"text": "Arsicault Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "French bakery with a petite, rustic interior & a pastry case for kouign-amann to scones & more.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kU2NrNXJWVXd3ZGpSbE4zVnROR3R2Tm14dE9HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "❤️❤️Hands down, I love their croissants and amazing atmosphere. You will find the bakery line before the actual bakery. It’s truly worth a bit of a wait. Line moves fast and you will experience this awesome bakery.  The kouign amann, ham and cheese, and almond 🥐are EPIC!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "❤️❤️Hands down, I love their croissants and amazing atmosphere. You will find the bakery line before the actual bakery. It’s truly worth a bit of a wait. Line moves fast and you will experience this awesome bakery.  The kouign amann, ham and cheese, and almond 🥐are EPIC!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Kevin Kammeyer", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116780678685322531247/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULZbSHfqSPmxmmQHKGqIEu44HRT0ZNBls4qPvKO6iDkkbOXq_cPA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-11T14:56:14.027512375Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kU2NrNXJWVXd3ZGpSbE4zVnROR3R2Tm14dE9HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21kU2NrNXJWVXd3ZGpSbE4zVnROR3R2Tm14dE9HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858739f45d4f27:0x2f0b49df0ee8b492"}, {"name": "places/ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jeFkwcHFZbXBUYWpSak1WZE9abXM0VlMxNVdXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Flaky buttery goodness. Wish croissants were $4-5 but for $6 not bad for sf. They only had chocolate and plain, hence the 4 star review;  quality was 5/5 and price 3/5 overall solid 4! Bon appetit! 🥐", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Flaky buttery goodness. Wish croissants were $4-5 but for $6 not bad for sf. They only had chocolate and plain, hence the 4 star review;  quality was 5/5 and price 3/5 overall solid 4! Bon appetit! 🥐", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alexander Mejia", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115424898898611619221/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWG1Cx_YYM7SezP1L8dweCXRLrsn9eSHwXWki80mgxDdyfViM8c0Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-28T21:48:06.878851625Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jeFkwcHFZbXBUYWpSak1WZE9abXM0VlMxNVdXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jeFkwcHFZbXBUYWpSak1WZE9abXM0VlMxNVdXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858739f45d4f27:0x2f0b49df0ee8b492"}, {"name": "places/ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jdGVFWkNVbWg1TkhSUlRHZEZaVVp5U1RoRU9HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Wanted to come to this bakery since I heard they have the best almond croissants. I was so happy I finally made it, the chocolate almond croissants are the best. The line is not bad at all for a Sunday early afternoon. When I got the croissant, it felt heavy. I was worried it would be too heavy, but no, the filling is smooth and perfect, croissant is buttery and perfect layered, it literally melts in the mouth. The cranberry coconut scone is very good as well. The ones I enjoyed most is plain croissant, light, puffy, perfect.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Wanted to come to this bakery since I heard they have the best almond croissants. I was so happy I finally made it, the chocolate almond croissants are the best. The line is not bad at all for a Sunday early afternoon. When I got the croissant, it felt heavy. I was worried it would be too heavy, but no, the filling is smooth and perfect, croissant is buttery and perfect layered, it literally melts in the mouth. The cranberry coconut scone is very good as well. The ones I enjoyed most is plain croissant, light, puffy, perfect.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hua Mao", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107275032742992926250/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVnfP_-AMaMe5UzIeXVWU6DoxQWjQc6iU5mE5BzxzyY5uxVfLxi=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-16T15:09:06.025741776Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jdGVFWkNVbWg1TkhSUlRHZEZaVVp5U1RoRU9HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25jdGVFWkNVbWg1TkhSUlRHZEZaVVp5U1RoRU9HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858739f45d4f27:0x2f0b49df0ee8b492"}, {"name": "places/ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ReFpVcENiRlJRTmtWMlgzUldVek5mYWs1TWJuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I don’t like waiting in line because I’m a snarky New Yorker, but the croissants here were really good. I was in line listening to joggers boasting about their easy lives and also how good this place was, so I decided to wait and it didn’t disappoint. Gotta try the chocolate and regular croissants!\n\nSorry for the knock sfers, I couldn’t help myself!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I don’t like waiting in line because I’m a snarky New Yorker, but the croissants here were really good. I was in line listening to joggers boasting about their easy lives and also how good this place was, so I decided to wait and it didn’t disappoint. Gotta try the chocolate and regular croissants!\n\nSorry for the knock sfers, I couldn’t help myself!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "William Chu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108544296790248540177/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpsezFRGH_q9qPpmkzIC8z8q_w2zSAsLQJBsL5t6_q0jQGF2Tr=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-19T14:53:56.733643028Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ReFpVcENiRlJRTmtWMlgzUldVek5mYWs1TWJuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ReFpVcENiRlJRTmtWMlgzUldVek5mYWs1TWJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858739f45d4f27:0x2f0b49df0ee8b492"}, {"name": "places/ChIJJ09d9DmHhYARkrToDt9JCy8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GRVJGb3djRFZFV25SMGRFRmZSa1prVEhWMFFXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Amazing almond croissant — super buttery, flaky, and totally worth it. Go early to get the fresh batch; we waited about 15–20 minutes in line, but it moved fast. Definitely one of the best almond croissants I’ve had!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Amazing almond croissant — super buttery, flaky, and totally worth it. Go early to get the fresh batch; we waited about 15–20 minutes in line, but it moved fast. Definitely one of the best almond croissants I’ve had!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "vamsi C", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110443144189514634250/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWEzWvALC0xMBO_V1DIJFSUf2ITEWirGRppX9zVLxb2_Ih9g09=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2025-11-02T20:02:40.237319533Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZEN